@startuml
title Moment → Insight → Practice → Guidance  (example: Export Report)
actor User
participant UI
participant "Behavior API" as BEH
database "InsightStore" as INS
collections "PracticeAgg" as PRA
participant "Recommender" as REC

User -> UI: Perform action (Scenario step)
UI -> BEH: POST /behavior/moment {moment}
activate BEH
BEH -> INS: updateInsight(user, actor, key, delta)
INS --> BEH: insight{confidence,status}
deactivate BEH

... periodic or streaming ...
BEH -> PRA: aggregate(actor)  # k-anon filter
PRA --> BEH: practice{patterns,guardrails,hints}

== Request guidance ==
UI -> REC: GET /behavior/guidance?actor&usecase&context
activate REC
REC -> PRA: fetch(actor.practice)
REC -> INS: check user veto (Contested?)
REC --> UI: hints/defaults (scored)
deactivate REC

User -> UI: Accept / Undo
UI -> BEH: POST /behavior/feedback {momentId, type, strength}
@enduml
